Mocminer is a DMKD toolkit written in Perl to mine and translate non-western corpus, 
discover topics, and the sentiment toward them.

More documentation will come as I clean up this kit.

INSTALLATION:

1) Set the DB up
mysql -u mocminer -p mocminer < mocminer.sql

2) Install required perl libraries.

  perl -MCPAN -e shell
  install Encode::HanConvert
  install Encode::HanExtra
  install Lingua::Translate
  install Lingua::Translate::Google

3) Install plda

4) ./start.pl ...
